name: Safe Fur Work
description:
This model is a finetune of the base SD 1.5 trained on 370,000 safe:rated images from e621 using EveryDream2trainer.

This model is still in training but after 4.5 Epochs taking 3 days to train its finally at a usable level and will be farther improved in the future.

Use e621 tags for prompting most should work (other the the nsfw ones)

Well sometimes give real animal photos try adding feral to the negative prompt and add ((anthro)) to the regular if this keeps happening.

Fun tags to mess around with: realistic, photorealism, photo manipulation
